  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nUbuntu-server binaries better to be generated during build because their replacing requires a lot of manual work: generating new binaries, uploading them to servers, changing hashes in nix files.\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\nHere are steps that needed to generate binaries:\r\n1) pkg package should be installed - https://github.com/zeit/pkg\r\n`npm install -g pkg`\r\n\r\n2) yarn install should happen before next steps \r\n\r\n3) Patch should be applied to realm file:\r\n`patch node_modules/realm/lib/index.js < patches/change_realm_for_pkg.patch`\r\n`patch file can be found here - https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/8244`\r\n\r\n4) Binaries should be generated with pkg:\r\n`pkg ubuntu-server.js --targets macos --out-path ./ubuntu-server-binary/macos`\r\n`pkg ubuntu-server.js --targets linux --out-path ./ubuntu-server-binary/linux`\r\n`pkg ubuntu-server.js --targets win --out-path ./ubuntu-server-binary/win`\r\n\r\n5) Realm patch should be reverted:\r\n`patch -R node_modules/realm/lib/index.js < patches/change_realm_for_pkg.patch`\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\n## Future Steps\r\n\r\nubuntu-server binaries should be removed from servers\r\n",
